{"tid":2473970,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［NBA] 今年金塊好大機會入finals","createTime":"2021-04-03T15:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T16:36:03.000Z","uid":51738,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e1026ba6122589ee8f2d74ef5cf392c8b083adb1","tid":2473970,"uid":51738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"睇勻全league入面一前一後雙引擎陣容，金塊最fit<br />\n<br />\n先講球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJokic 喺策應同籃底方面好強，今年mvp 熱門人選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMurray 入PO會爆seed ，切入/ 三分/ 切入再傳都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAG 做角色球色係夠做有突，防守再做好啲已經係bonus<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMPJ 呢位小將都值得期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋呢隊金塊已經有足夠季後賽經驗，陣容核心冇大改<br />\n<br />\n上年亦打過晒湖人同快艇兩隊奪冠熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n睇返西岸其他強隊（前六）<br />\n<br />\n今年湖人兩巨傷晒，季後賽唔知可以走幾完，仲要冇咗兩大奪冠功臣 RR9 同猴活，衛冕之路難免崎嶇(上年係靠猴活ko jokic)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJazz 戰績睇落好靚仔，但唔好唔記得兩億先生上年俾jokic 收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，加上季後賽節奏一定變慢，我諗jazz 入到po 可能二輪遊<br />\n<br />\n太陽今年有cp3 carry 即刻擠身強隊之列<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係整體季後賽經驗不足。船長都唔後生，體力未必夠頂，入到po 都未必過到2輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/scheme.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再講 LAC ，其實我睇好LAC 入西決，但問題都係放喺雙星身上，領導力不足。<br />\n雖然補咗RR9 但講真同RR9夾唔到的話係會出事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拓荒者...雙刃劍一把<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攻擊力好強，但冇防守，絕對唔睇好...<br />\n<br />\n最後，西岸邊隊入finals都好，最緊要收宇宙網皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"208122617127b4c18ef6c268cd474baca35beea5","tid":2473970,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e1026ba6122589ee8f2d74ef5cf392c8b083adb1","tid":2473970,"uid":51738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-03T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"睇勻全league入面一前一後雙引擎陣容，金塊最fit<br />\n<br />\n先講球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJokic 喺策應同籃底方面好強，今年mvp 熱門人選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMurray 入PO會爆seed ，切入/ 三分/ 切入再傳都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAG 做角色球色係夠做有突，防守再做好啲已經係bonus<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMPJ 呢位小將都值得期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋呢隊金塊已經有足夠季後賽經驗，陣容核心冇大改<br />\n<br />\n上年亦打過晒湖人同快艇兩隊奪冠熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash